content.rendered:
BOSS AIR AIRBAG 2600 COMPLETE

Boss Air Airbag 2600 Complete available for order now through Automax 4×4! Order online, come in & see us or give us a call on (02) 6699 2744 for a quote!

This product has a double bellow bag, approx 186mm diameter, 1181KG @100psi.

Includes:

  • 2600lb Extreme Series Bag
  • Top and Bottom plate and stainless bolts.
  • 12 countersunk stainless bolts

Fully compressed – 65mm with 6mm ends fitted
Max diameter – 190mm (widest when fully compressed)
Max height- 250mm
Max working pressure 0-160 psi
Test pressure – 480psi
Burst pressure – 1000psi

To view the full range of Boss Air products available, CLICK HERE!

For more 4×4 inspiration follow us on Instagram and Facebook
